<body>
    <h1>New-Hire (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC02)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"New-Hire(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC02)-New-Hireworkflo=
w">New-Hire workflow</h3>
<p>Table-18</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"3=
36da9b6-3cd0-4780-b07f-1001c31c3d12" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 221.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1576.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>New-Hire</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The New-Hire use case describes the process for access provided upon hir=
ing, including birthright access and other applicable downstream applicatio=
ns.&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the solution design docum=
ent.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Assignment Status&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hire Date&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry&nbsp;</p></li>
</ol>
<p></p>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>User has gone through the pre-hire process and their identity object and=
 account data are present in SailPoint IdentityIQ</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Start Date should match with Current Date.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Assignment status</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should be=
 equal to =E2=80=98<strong>Active - Payroll Eligible</strong>=E2=80=99.</p>=
</li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>Worker Type</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should be equal=
 to =E2=80=98<strong>Employee</strong>=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98<strong>User Action</strong>=E2=80=99 attribute should be equal=
 to =E2=80=98<strong>Hire</strong>=E2=80=99&nbsp;</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ to update the additional access needed for AD.</p><=
/li>
<li>
<p>Azure accounts will be updated based on AD updates via Azure AD Sync.</p=
></li>
<li>
<p>Birthright access to be provisioned based on the user=E2=80=99s profile =
details.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will notify the user and user=E2=80=99s manager thr=
ough email for successful processing of the joiner process.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, GSuite, ServiceNow, Oracle ERP Cloud, Oracle EP=
M Cloud, OCI</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ should provision additional birthright access based=
 on the user updated profile data.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"921" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"bc=
81b07b-0267-4e7c-92e5-84a036c4a6cb" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 85.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 149.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 687.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required in the Basic Flow</p>
<p>Ascension Health Alliance team to confirm on notification templates</p><=
/td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ascension Health Alliance team to confirm the list of birthright access =
applications based on demographic data</p>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to provide users=E2=80=99 demographic =
information and access mapping for pre-hire:</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
